#Sticky Footer Working Using Flexbox
  #HTML
    <body class="Site">
      <header>…</header>
      <main class="Site-content">…</main>
      <footer>…</footer>
    </body>
  #CSS
    .Site {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .Site-content {
      flex: 1;
    }
